# Copy to .dev.vars for local `wrangler dev` / `wrangler dev --test-scheduled`.
# Never commit the real values (.dev.vars is gitignored).
#
# The HRPT sync's storage backend is Cloudflare D1 (see the `d1_databases`
# binding in wrangler.jsonc), accessed via the `env.DB` Workers binding —
# not a REST URL + bearer token, so there is no secret to set here for it.
# `wrangler dev` automatically provisions a local D1 simulation for the
# `DB` binding; run `wrangler d1 migrations apply spordo-hrpt --local` once
# to apply migrations/0001_init.sql to it.
#
# (No vars currently required here. This file is kept as the place to add
# any future local-dev secrets.)
